00:15:24.380 --> 00:15:29.470
in a safe and clean environment.

00:15:29.470 --> 00:15:34.160
So, this obviously brings us to where we are
today.

00:15:34.160 --> 00:15:39.339
And again, if you guys have ever been to Delancey
Street or Lower East Side, you're familiar

00:15:39.339 --> 00:15:42.410
with the fact that the streetscape isn't really
very friendly.

00:15:42.410 --> 00:15:47.279
It's really not very fun and it's actually
quite dangerous to spend quality time on Delancey

00:15:47.279 --> 00:15:51.980
Street, particularly in this part of Delancey
Street.

00:15:51.980 --> 00:15:59.410
So, this is again a lot of our motivation
on why this particular project has come to

00:15:59.410 --> 00:16:00.600
where we are.

00:16:00.600 --> 00:16:06.990
This is another slide that helps point out
