00:17:38.739 --> 00:17:41.320
beneath the surface, right at the foot of
the Williamsburg Bridge.

00:17:41.320 --> 00:17:47.840
So, in a lot of ways, this made a perfect
site for us to look at to actually turn into

00:17:47.840 --> 00:17:49.269
a public amenity.

00:17:49.269 --> 00:17:51.960
And that's the goal of what we're trying to
accomplish here.

00:17:51.960 --> 00:17:55.809
Now, you saw the pictures that we were just
looking at before, like the one on the bottom

00:17:55.809 --> 00:17:57.470
