to what I think Dan is leading into about

00:47:51.930 --> 00:47:54.430
being able to have alternate uses for daytime,
nighttime, other times, etcetera.

00:47:54.430 --> 00:47:55.430
&gt;&gt;Dan Barasch: New York's hottest club.

00:47:55.430 --> 00:47:56.430
[laughter]
&gt;&gt;James Ramsey: Right.

