00:52:33.786 --> 00:52:34.786
Are you on Clinton between Delancey and--?

00:52:34.786 --> 00:52:35.786
&gt;&gt;MALE #7: Between Staten Road.

00:52:35.786 --> 00:52:37.440
&gt;&gt;James Ramsey: If you go one block south,
there is a bar called Second Floor on Clinton

00:52:37.440 --> 00:52:40.329
